summary: Replaces several sounds the Draugr make with sounds from the Tourettes Guy! It makes the eight million burial sites you have to dig through for quests more fun!
descriptionHtml:
Hello everyone! Thank you for taking a look at my first mod!

This mod replaces 13 sounds in total for the Draugr with sounds from the legendary Tourettes Guy! Have fun!
author: KamikazeTheGreat
